        </article>
        <article class="rounded-[2rem] bg-white p-7">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">Accessibility</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-[var(--ht-night-60)]">Semantic <code>&lt;time&gt;</code>, fallback text, <code>datetime</code>, titles, visible focus states, and polite live regions.</p>
